# Project Instructions — solarx-tuya-integration

> This file is read by Windsurf IDE AI assistant.

## Project Root

All source code is inside the current directory (`smart-charge-glow/` is the project root when opened directly).

## Commands

```bash
bun dev          # Start dev server
bun build        # Production build (Nitro + Vercel)
bun lint         # ESLint
bun format       # Prettier
```

## Tech Stack

- **Framework**: TanStack Start (full-stack React 19)
- **Routing**: @tanstack/react-router (file-based, `src/routes/`)
- **Data**: @tanstack/react-query + server functions
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS v4
- **UI**: Radix UI + shadcn/ui (`src/components/ui/`)
- **Charts**: Recharts | **Forms**: React Hook Form + Zod
- **Server**: Nitro → Vercel | **IoT**: Tuya Cloud API
- **Language**: TypeScript strict (no `any`, no `@ts-ignore`)

## Key Files

