## Rules

- `@/` → `src/` path alias
- Tuya API calls: server-side only (`'use server'`)
- Never edit `routeTree.gen.ts`
- Never add duplicate plugins to `vite.config.ts`
- **Lovable connected**: never force push / rebase pushed commits

